reviews.review_text: Re : Confused My assumption is that this is the 44.1 version meant for CD burning as 121125 is listed as 48 in the name of the fileset ...  But that's just my guess
A gem This is a really special show.  Strange sets with lots of covers.  I don't know... there's something about this show...
Early & Late Shows Plus 2 sets of NRPS.  A smoking hot evening, band is on!  Some good stage banter, with Pig's entertaining raps in Lovelight to wrap up the night.
